  "texts": [
    "For the development of the protocol, it was observed that, on average, most respondents find this stage neutral.",
    "For the search phase, 22 (36.7%) of the respondents rated this stage as difficult, while 6 (10%) rated this stage as extremely difficult.",
    "Both 15 (25%) rated this stage as neutral and easy; thus, the level of ease is likewise neutral but more complex, with a mean value of 3.25.",
    "For the title and abstract screening, 31 (51.7%) of the respondents rated this stage as easy, while 13 (21.7%) rated this stage as complex.",
    "The mean rank was 2.57, indicating that most respondents consider this stage easy."
  ]
}